 Home  »  Blogs  »  DevOps in the Cloud  »  Are VMs becoming El Caminos? Are VMs becoming El Caminos? 
 By  Rob Hirschfeld  on  March 6, 2015 14 Comments   In 2010, it looked as if virtualization had won. We expected all servers to virtualize workloads and the primary question was which cloud infrastructure manager would dominate. Now in 2015, the picture is not as clear. I’m seeing a trend that threatens the “virtualize all things” battle cry.   
 
 
 
  
